products.title: Premium Sleek Jet Faux Wood Blind - 50mm Slat
products.description: Dark and dramatic, this premium sleek jet faux wood blind is quite the smart choice. The smooth, matt finish oozes sophistication, whilst the black colourway is just superb. And since it's made of faux wood, this blind is as practical as they come. It's waterproof, wont warp and dark and dramatic, this premium sleek jet faux wood blind is quite the smart choice.
